ug 10, 2014","formatted_time":"6:33 PM","body":"Special Offer: Try a Times Digital Subscription for\nJust $5 for 12 Weeks\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------\n\nView in browser:\nhttp://e.newyorktimesinfo.com/a/tBT50KlB81HXJB87rWfAAwENc$4/viwb?t_params=CAMPAIGN_CODE%3D48WWF%26EMAIL%3Djeeproject%2540yahoo.com%26REGI_ID%3D47275261\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-- THE NEW YORK TIMES --\n\nTHE WORLD'S FINEST JOURNALISM\nJUST $5 FOR 12 WEEKS ON A DIGITAL SUBSCRIPTION\n\nREDEEM SPECIAL OFFER:\nhttp://e.newyorktimesinfo.com/a/tBT50KlB81HXJB87rWfAAwENc$4/sub01t\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------\n\nUncompromising integrity. Unrivaled coverage. All with an \nunlimited subscription to NYTimes.com and NYTimes apps; just $5 \nfor your first 12 weeks. Plus, you now get the new NYT Opinion \napp, included free with your subscription, bringing you a wide \narray of the most compelling opinion pieces anywhere, all in \none place, curated by our editors. You'll also get the NYT \nNow app, featuring news summaries when you're pressed for \ntime and daily briefings to give you a look at the day ahead. \nThis offer is for registered users only, so subscribe now \nand never miss a story important to you.\n\nREDEEM SPECIAL OFFER:\nhttp://e.newyorktimesinfo.com/a/tBT50KlB81HXJB87rWfAAwENc$4/sub02t\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------\n\nFor just $5 for 12 weeks, get unlimited access to:\n\n-- Immersive Storytelling by world-class journalists\n\n-- Best-in-Class Apps such as the new NYT Now\n\n-- Innovative Multimedia on topics that inspire you most\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------\n\nThis email was sent to you as a registered user on NYTimes.com. \n\nDoes not include e-reader editions, Times Premier content or \nThe New York Times Crossword. Mobile apps are not supported \non all devices. Other restrictions may apply.\n\nTo ensure delivery of emails from The New York Times, please\nadd nytimes@e.newyorktimesinfo.com to your address book.\n\nThe New York Times:\nhttp://e.newyorktimesinfo.com/a/tBT50KlB81HXJB87rWfAAwENc$4/nyt\n\nPrivacy Policy:\nhttp://e.newyorktimesinfo.com/a/tBT50KlB81HXJB87rWfAAwENc$4/privacy\n\nContact Us:\nhelp@nytimes.com\n\nUnsubscribe:\nhttp://e.newyorktimesinfo.com/a/tBT50KlB81HXJB87rWfAAwENc$4/unsub?email=jeeproject@yahoo.com&REGI_ID=47275261\n\n(c) 2014 The New York Times Company \nP.O. Box 8041, Davenport, IA 52808-8041\n\n","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN\"\n\t\"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd\"><html><head><title>Special Offer: Try a Times Digital Subscription for Just $5 for 12 \nWeeks</title></head><body onload=''>\n\n\n\n\n<!-- 48WWF -->\n\n<!-- 100% TABLE -->\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"100%\">\n<!-- NYT LOGO/VIEW BROWSER TABLE -->\n\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"font-family:Helvetica, Arial, Sans \nSerif;color:#ffffff;font-size:12px;line-height:125%;\" align=\"left\" \nvalign=\"middle\" width=\"500\">Special Offer: Try \na Times Digital Subscription for Just $5 for 12 Weeks</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"middle\" width=\"189\"><a \nhref=\"http://e.newyorktimesinfo.com/a/hBT50KlB81HXJB87rWfAAwENc$4/nyt\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"display:block\" \nsrc=\"http://f.e.newyorktimesinfo.com/i/18/2094298569/20140715_14-1270_CoreDigiTestEmail_DigiCore_nytlogo_189x45.gif\" \nalt=\"The New York Times\" border=\"0\" height=\"45\" width=\"189\"></a></td>\n<td style=\"font-family:Helvetica, Arial, Sans \nSerif;color:#397aaf;font-size:12px;line-height:125%;\" align=\"right\" \nvalign=\"bottom\" width=\"411\"><a \nhref=\"htt